replies.body:
{{champion:32}} 
More solid theme as the "Don't Come Near Me or Be Punished Heavily" Tank. He should have the most harm to an enemy champion for coming near him of the Tanks.

{{champion:89}} 
Heard many (not just you) wanting her to get some love to make her good in more Solo roles

{{champion:54}} 
Make him more than just an ultimate and move his niche away from Rammus

{{champion:57}} 
Preferably be more about his E, perhaps being the "Vision" Tank in the game through sapling scouts

{{champion:111}} 
Potential adjustments to his Q to slightly differentiate him from the rest of the hook characters

{{champion:33}} 
Solidify his role as the "Armor Tank"

{{champion:113}} 
Make her a much more aggressive Tank that revolves around intense slows and perhaps Grounded effects

{{champion:154}} 
Make his Q and W more interesting, especially his Q which doesn't really flow well with the rest of the kit
